title: Norwegian language pack for Windows XP Media Center Edition
description:
Since I lost my original cd with this file, I have searched hard for this on the net, and thanks to those who shared it with me. So, here it is for you others who need it, to convert your english Windows XP Media Center Edition 2005 to Norwegian.

Hint: Install ALL windows updates before using this, excluding Internet exporer 7.0.
